The diffusion chamber located in a magnetic field
with a strength of 1.5 T was used. The chamber was
irradiated with bremsstrahlung gamma-quanta, which had
the maximal energy of 150 MeV. With the aim
of reducing the target density, the chamber was filled
with a methane-helium mixture in the proportion
1 : 7 up to a pressure of 1.5 atm.
